  "body": "# Problem\r\n`status-im.ui.screens.offline-messaging-settings.views` and a few other screens in sync settings use a switch that seems to be a leftover. All other components use the Quo switch view.\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n  <summary>View screenshots</summary>\r\n\r\n| Quo Switch  | Old (probably native) switch | \r\n|---|---|\r\n|![Screenshot_20210706-155026_Status Debug](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1925158/124585162-aae98200-de72-11eb-8f99-988db1604be0.jpg) | ![Screenshot_20210706-155035_Status Debug](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1925158/124585200-b472ea00-de72-11eb-9ca0-ae174902c129.jpg) |\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n</details>\r\n\r\nThe older switches are probably native and look different from the Quo switches. The difference is significant on Android. \r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\nReplace the old switches with new list items.\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nAll switches should look consistent with Quo.\r\n",
